    "119563415": {
      "title": "CP violation in B meson decays",
      "abstract": "After a short introduction on CP asymmetries in K and B meson decays, I discuss a few recent results related to CP violation, mainly from the BABAR experiment: CPT tests in ${\\rm B}^0\\bar{\\rm B}^0$ mixing, search for CP violation in ${\\rm b}\\to {\\rm c}\\bar{\\rm c}{\\rm d}$ and ${\\rm b}\\to {\\rm s}\\bar{\\rm s}{\\rm s}$ decays, and measurements of the unitarity-triangle angle α in B→ππ and B→ρρ decays. I conclude with the result of a CKM-matrix fit to all relevant observations."
